    <abstract>Concerning Mount Gang, Miao Quansun lists "Five sections of rock cut inscriptions at
        Mount Gang": Section 1 corresponds to GS_A4; section 2 corresponds to GS_B30; section 3, a
        "Buddhist sūtra in 21 lines" is unclear, but might correspond to the inscriptions on Chicken
        Beak Rock; section 4 corresponds to GS_A3; section 5 corresponds to GS_A5. Concerning "Minor
        Mount Tie", Miao has only two short entries for Tie_1 and Tie_2.</abstract>
